snippet.title: How to Install a Chamberlain Wall Mount Garage Door Opener, Model RJO20
snippet.description:
This video demonstrates how to install a Chamberlain wall mount garage door opener, model RJO20.

For more information about the Chamberlain products covered in this video, please reference the following articles: 
Manual: http://bit.ly/RJO20Manual
Quick Start Guide: http://bit.ly/RJO20QuickStartGuide

This video also applies to the following models: RJO20C

Additional Resources:
Technical Support: http://bit.ly/ChamberlainTechSupport
Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/chamberlainsupport

Still need help? Contact Chamberlain Technical Support: http://bit.ly/ContactChamberlainSupport
